devdoc.author: Eduardo Suarez Ojeda
devdoc.details: The Contract that controls all the Insurances created in the node and groups them by hotel.

MergeBytes(bytes,bytes).details: Returns the array result of the concatenation.

addInsurance(address).details: Modify the mappings that link hotels and insurances.

getAddressOfInsurance(bytes32).details: Useful to call insurance method in that address if needed.

getAllInsurances().details: Returns a serialized array of bytes with the content of all insurances.

getHotelInsurancesData(bytes32).details: Returns a serialized array of bytes with the content of all insurances.
